<br>
This new spell line will help in velius a great deal. I know some people say you can just have all melees attack on one side of the mob (eg, a dragon) to stop it gating, but in my experience that method is very hit and miss, and in many instances causes raid wipe out. It is not reliable, not consistant, and people tend to avoid certain gating mobs just so that they aren't systematically summoned to it for their turn at being killed.<br>
<br>
