4. I'll take this new line of spells thanks.<br>
<br>
I hope they dont make them spell drops or their usual almost impossible wizard quest approach. These should be on that vendor in Sol Ro temple or something, just like they made the class balancing spells for dr00ds and mages available on vendors.<br>
